    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-80ec-88f2-c5328210504b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors formalize group formation as a mathematical problem and use Variable Neighborhood Search to form heterogenous groups in a collaborative setting. VNS was compared against the best results obtained by other optimization methods (CPLEX). ",
