    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-8046-a16f-d1ccfd876f2d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To show effectiveness, the authors took 3 groups of college students and, inside each group, used different algorithms to form teams of 4 in a Calculus course. Students in groups created with VNS outperformed their peers in groups formed randomly. However, the VNS groups did noty outperform the groups following ontological guidelines.  ",
